commitResults.messageTitle: Level 0. Rename, Greet, Exit. Deleted Duke.java, replaced with Jarvis.java and edited Jarvis.java
Level 1. Echo Added logic to echo user commands. If user enters anything other than bye, echo. If user enters bye, reply with goodbye message.
Level 2. Add, List. Added logic to store tasks and print out a list of tasks when the request "list" is given.
Level 3. Mark as Done. Added Task.java. Added logic for "mark" and "unmark"
Level 4. ToDos, Events, Deadlines Added Todo.java, Event.java and Dealine.java which inherit from Task.java Added logic in Jarvis.java to handle "todo", "event" and "deadline" commands
